festival.title: Sublian Festival
festival.description: -The Sublian festival, a two weeklong celebration which culminates every year on the 23rd of July, is rooted in the Batangueños’ devotion to the town’s patron: the Holy Cross in Bauan and Agoncillo, and the Sto. Niño in Batangas City.
